# Benchmarking papers

```
Jorge, E., Foissac, S., Neuvial, P., Zytnicki, M., & Vialaneix, N. (2025). A comprehensive review and benchmark of differential analysis tools for Hi-C data. Briefings in Bioinformatics, 26(2), bbaf074.

Zheng, Y., Zhou, P., & Keleş, S. (2021). FreeHi-C spike-in simulations for benchmarking differential chromatin interaction detection. Methods, 189, 3-11.

```

# Tools references


```
diffHiC:

Lun ATL, Smyth GK (2015). “diffHic: a Bioconductor package to detect differential genomic interactions in Hi-C data.” BMC Bioinformatics, 16, 258.

[diffHiC](https://www.bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/diffHic.html)

```

```
HiCcompare:

Stansfield JC, Cresswell KG, Vladimirov VI, Dozmorov MG (2018). “HiCcompare: an R-package for joint normalization and comparison of HI-C datasets.” BMC Bioinformatics, 19(1). doi:10.1186/s12859-018-2288-x, https://github.com/dozmorovlab/HiCcompare.

[HiCcompare](https://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/HiCcompare.html)

```

```
multiHiCcompare:

Stansfield JC, Cresswell KG, Dozmorov MG (2019). “multiHiCcompare: joint normalization and comparative analysis of complex Hi-C experiments.” Bioinformatics, 35(17). doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btz048, https://github.com/dozmorovlab/multiHiCcompare.

[multiHiCcompare](https://www.bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/multiHiCcompare.html)
```


# Installying independent libraries 

```
ml R/4.5.2-mba

#Initialized on 
cd ./HiC-Dip/benchmarking/

RScript
dir.create("./diffHiC_Rlibs",recursive=TRUE)
.libPaths("./diffHiC_Rlibs")

if (!require("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")

BiocManager::install("diffHic")


```

```
ml R/4.5.2-mba

dir.create("./HiCcompare_Rlibs",recursive=TRUE)
.libPaths("./HiCcompare_Rlibs")

if (!require("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")

BiocManager::install("HiCcompare")
```
